# Sage system

This project uses the **Sage** SDLC agent system.

Always read [Agents.md](../../Agents.md) first. It is the root contract linked to all phase agents in `agents/`.

When doing SDLC work, use `/sage-*` slash commands. Set `workflow_profile` in manifest per [workflows/profiles.md](../../workflows/profiles.md).

Do not skip phases except those listed in `manifest.skipped_phases`. Never skip plan, build, qa, or release.

Agent registry and flow: see the top of Agents.md.
